channel.title: StaticX - New server
channel.description:
Thanks for looking people. To start off with, The new server called Staticx has all you rsps needs. We have some minigames including a zombie minigame, pest control, barrows, dual arena and more. We have dragon claws, vesta, statius, primal, death cape, dark bow, bandos, katagon, torva, armadyl, chaotics, pernix, promethium, celestial, gorgonite, virtus, flameburst defender, all skill capes including a completionist cape, lord marshal, staff of light, spirit bloom robes, runic, all spirit shields including spectral and elysian, dagon hai, hand cannon, dragonfire shield, and every other item you can imagine. if we dont have it, tell us and we will add it. We have dungeoneering and summoning with working pets. skill island, same old classic edgeville home with atleast 25 different shops. Player owned shops. Staff spots are open and available.
GO TO thestaticgame.com TO LEARN MORE, OR DOWNLOAD OUR CLIENT AT thestaticgame.com/client.jar AND LOGIN AND PLAY. ITS SIMPLE AS THAT.
If you have any questions about the game message me on here or message "Staticx" and "Marlboro" ingame.
IF YOU DONT HAVE ANYTHING GOOD TO SAY ABOUT THIS SERVER THEN TAKE IT SOMEWHERE ELSE. WE ARE AN ASSHOLE-FREE COMMUNITY. THANK YOU AND HAVE A NICE DAY.
